data.description: Discover this inviting home for sale in Cumming, featuring a seller contribution of $5000 toward closing cost! Located in a highly sought-after cul-de-sac, this stunning residence boasts an array of desirable features that cater to modern lifestyles. With its prime location feeding into the esteemed Denmark High School district, this property presents an exceptional opportunity for families seeking quality education and a vibrant community atmosphere.    As you enter through the grand two-story foyer, you're greeted by an atmosphere of elegance and warmth. The main level showcases a meticulously designed kitchen adorned with luxurious Quartz countertops, complemented by sleek stainless steel appliances, and enhanced with freshly painted interiors, exuding a contemporary allure. The spacious layout seamlessly transitions into the inviting living spaces, perfect for both intimate gatherings and entertaining guests.    Retreat to the main level master suite, offering a serene sanctuary for relaxation and rejuvenation. Upstairs, discover three additional bedrooms and a full bath, providing ample space for family members or guests.    The lower level of this home presents a unique opportunity with a fully equipped rental suite featuring a bedroom, full bath, living area, kitchen, bonus room, and a private exterior entrance. Whether for extended family members, guests, or potential rental income, this versatile space offers endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle needs.    Outside, enjoy the charm of the neighborhood amenity area, complete with a refreshing pool and well-maintained tennis courts, ideal for leisurely afternoons spent outdoors. Additionally, the convenience of being just moments away from Highway 400, Fowler Park, shopping destinations, and a diverse array of restaurants ensures that every need is effortlessly met.    Don't miss the chance to make this property your new home, where every day offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury living. Schedule your private tour today and experience the epitome of Cumming, GA, living at its finest.
